settings.heading: What products/services do you offer?
settings.row_content: We offer a wide range of high-quality products/services designed to meet different customer needs. All items are carefully selected to ensure quality, reliability, and value.

settings.heading: How can I place an order?
settings.row_content: You can place an order directly through our website by selecting your desired product, adding it to the cart, and completing the checkout process.

settings.heading: Do you offer international shipping?
settings.row_content: Yes, we offer international shipping to selected countries. Shipping charges and delivery times may vary depending on your location.

settings.heading: How long does delivery take?
settings.row_content: Delivery usually takes 3–7 business days for domestic orders and 7–14 business days for international orders, depending on the destination.

settings.heading: What payment methods do you accept?
settings.row_content: We accept major credit/debit cards, UPI, net banking, and other secure online payment methods.

settings.heading: Can I track my order?
settings.row_content: Yes, once your order is shipped, you will receive a tracking link via email or SMS to monitor your delivery status.

settings.heading: What is your return policy?
settings.row_content: We offer a hassle-free return policy. If you are not satisfied with your purchase, you can request a return within a specified period as per our return guidelines.

settings.heading: Are your products safe and authentic?
settings.row_content: Yes, all our products are sourced from trusted suppliers and go through strict quality checks to ensure authenticity and safety.
